                    }
                ]
            },
            "solution": [
                {
                    "lang": "eng",
                    "value": "Upgrade to a version of BIND containing a fix for the memory leak.\n\n >=   BIND 9.11.5-P4\n >=   BIND 9.12.3-P4\n"
